_sText:
This map is a dev texture map, however, it contains some props.

Full Navmesh Support with painted place callouts (Tower, Bridge, Atrium, etc.)

Locations:
-CT Spawn
-T Spawn
-Bridge
-Tower
-Bombsite A
-Various sniping spots
-Various hiding spots
-A hefty amount of cover
-Func_breakable_surf (fragmenting glass) outside of T Spawn
-Decent Brushwork
-A couple of staircases
-Ladders at Tower and T Spawn
...and other things I am probably forgetting about.

This is my first published map, please point out any issues. I will try to fix them in the next version.

Thanks for playtesting!
